[{"location":"#ArtifactWrappers.jl","page":"Home","title":"ArtifactWrappers.jl","text":"","category":"section"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"A lightweight wrapper around Julia Artifacts.","category":"page"},{"location":"","page":"Home","title":"Home","text":"ArtifactWrappers.ArtifactFile\nArtifactWrappers.get_data_folder\nArtifactWrappers.ArtifactWrapper","category":"page"},{"location":"#ArtifactWrappers.ArtifactFile","page":"Home","title":"ArtifactWrappers.ArtifactFile","text":"ArtifactFile\n\nA single data file to be downloaded, containing both the url and the name to use locally.\n\nFields\n\nurl URL pointing to data to be downloaded\nfilename Local name used for downloaded online data\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"},{"location":"#ArtifactWrappers.get_data_folder","page":"Home","title":"ArtifactWrappers.get_data_folder","text":"get_data_folder(art_wrap::ArtifactWrapper)\n\nGet local folder of dataset defined in art_wrap.\n\nExample:\n\ndataset_path = get_data_folder(dataset)\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"function"},{"location":"#ArtifactWrappers.ArtifactWrapper","page":"Home","title":"ArtifactWrappers.ArtifactWrapper","text":"ArtifactWrapper\n\nA set of data files to be downloaded, grouped by data_name. Example:\n\ndataset = ArtifactWrapper(\n    @__DIR__,\n    isempty(get(ENV, \"CI\", \"\")),\n    \"MyDataSet\",\n    ArtifactFile[\n        ArtifactFile(\n            url=\"https://..../SomeNetCDF1.nc\",\n            filename=\"experiment1.nc\",\n        ),\n        ArtifactFile(\n            url=\"https://..../SomeNetCDF2.nc\",\n            filename=\"experiment2.nc\",\n        ),\n    ]\n)\n\nFields\n\nartifact_dir Directory to store artifact / data\nlocal_run Locally running (not using CI)\nartifact_toml Path to the used Artifacts.toml\ndata_name Unique name of dataset\nartifact_files Array of ArtifactFile's, grouped by this dataset\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"type"}]
